/idl_progs

Contains a variety of useful idl scripts for use with ExoCAM.  Note that my
original analysis langauge was IDL. But starting in spring 2023 I am migrating
to python to improve accessibility and engagement with scripts.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------
hybrid2pressure.pro       -- change hyrbid sigma coords to pressure
area_weighted_avg_gen.pro -- calculate area weighed average
changepress_cesm.pro      -- change the surface pressure in CAM .i. files
changevert_cesm.pro       -- change the numnber of vertical levels in CAM .i. files
mod_cesm_files.pro        -- modify/customize a smorgasboard 
landplanet_cesm_files.pro -- manipulate land planet initial files
haze_emission.pro         -- create carma haze emission file
carma_optics.pro          -- create carma optics files
